UPDATE lessons 
SET content_json = '{"verbatim_content": "Recommended Background\nThis project is designed for students who want hands-on control and embedded systems experience. You do not need a lot of experience, but some foundational knowledge is expected.\nRequired\n- Introductory programming experience in C++ or Python\n- Basic knowledge of electronics\nHelpful\n- Introductory exposure to embedded systems\n- Basic understanding of physics and signal theory\nIf you find that you are missing some of this background, reach out to us at support@shortcct.com and we can explore options to get you up to speed!", "source": "Ball and Beam Documentation for Kayla PDF"}'
